Tim and Ray have been doing webcomics for two years, so they put a little extra love into this excellent podcast. They touch on a good number of segments including Black Doom Award and REMIX!, and even ‘perform’ the bonus comic and reveal Toad’s 24-year-old mean-spirited secret.
